doctype html(lang='en')
head
    meta(charset='utf-8')  
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')  
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')  
    title IE8 Linter
    link(href='/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='/css/style.css', rel='stylesheet')
    style
      | html,body{height: 100%; width: 100%;}
body
  header 
    div.container
      form.linter-form.row 
        h1 IE8 Linter
        p Unfortunately for some of us, there are still projects out there that require compatability with our friendly dinosaur IE8. For these special occasions I made this little linter. What it does is spit all the usual suspects that cause incompatability and suggest fixes.
        div.row
          div.col-md-10
            input.form-control.input-lg(type="text", id="address", name="address", placeholder="Enter URL of the page you want to lint", value="#{address}")
          div.col-md-2
            button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(type="submit") Submit
  div.container
    if problems
      each problem in problems
        div.panel.panel-default
          div.panel-heading #{problem.problem}
          if problem.solution
            div.panel-body #{problem.solution}
  script(src='/js/jquery-2.1.3.min.js')
  script(src='/js/bootstrap.min.js')
